  <note reference-line="7" id="0">
    <original>vitthāretvā (sī. pī.)</original>
    <type>auto</type>
    <snippet>‘‘Tatrāvuso, yvāyaṃ puggalo aparisuddhakāyasamācāro parisuddhavacīsamācāro, kathaṃ tasmiṃ puggale āghāto paṭivinetabbo? Seyyathāpi, āvuso, bhikkhu paṃsukūliko rathiyāya nantakaṃ disvā vāmena pādena niggaṇhitvā dakkhiṇena pādena pattharitvā </snippet>
    <match>pattharitvā</match>
    <alternatives>
      <alternative source-abbr="sī." source="sri lanka">vitthāretvā</alternative>
      <alternative source-abbr="pī." source="pali text society">vitthāretvā</alternative>
    </alternatives>
  </note>
